Syndra collects Splinters of Wrath from gaining levels and damaging enemies which upgrade her abilities.<br><br><font color='#FF9900'>Dark Sphere</font>: Syndra can hold an additional charge<br><font color='#FF9900'>Force of Will</font>: Bonus true damage.<br><font color='#FF9900'>Scatter the Weak</font>: Increased width and slows all targets<br><font color='#FF9900'>Unleashed Power</font>: Executes low health targets